s://www.v2ex.com/u/licoycn", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "Licoy", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e72f/93ee/237505_mini.png?m=1769398487", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e72f/93ee/237505_normal.png?m=1769398487", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e72f/93ee/237505_large.png?m=1769398487", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e72f/93ee/237505_xlarge.png?m=1769398487", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e72f/93ee/237505_xxlarge.png?m=1769398487", "created": 1498570251, "last_modified": 1769398487, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "whiteleopard520", "last_touched": 1773419508, "title": "[抽奖] 为了庆祝 4 年的工具站重构上线&开源，抽 1 个 chatgpt team 车位", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1198203", "created": 1773448308, "deleted": 0, "content": "## 前言\r\n为了庆祝自己的工具站在 4 年没动的情况用 codex 一天重构换了血，也顺便开源了一下 ， 所以抽个奖\r\n\r\n**开源地址： https://github.com/Licoy/utils.fun**\r\n\r\n**在线使用：[https://utils.fun]( https://utils.fun)**\r\n\r\n（如果觉得站点不错可以给个小小的 star✨）\r\n\r\n## 抽奖内容\r\nchatgpt team 车位 * 1 ，1 个月无质保\r\n\r\n## 开奖时间\r\n北京时间 3 月 14 晚 23 点\r\n\r\n## 抽奖条件\r\n评论即可参与抽奖，多次评论只会最早一次的评论生效\r\n\r\n![]( https://github.com/Licoy/utils.fun/raw/main/docs/index.png)", "content_rendered": "<h2>前言</h2>\n<p>为了庆祝自己的工具站在 4 年没动的情况用 codex 一天重构换了血，也顺便开源了一下 ， 所以抽个奖</p>\n<p><strong>开源地址： <a href=\"https://github.com/Licoy/utils.fun\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/Licoy/utils.fun</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>在线使用：<a href=\"https://utils.fun\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://utils.fun</a></strong></p>\n<p>（如果觉得站点不错可以给个小小的 star✨）</p>\n<h2>抽奖内容</h2>\n<p>chatgpt team 车位 * 1 ，1 个月无质保</p>\n<h2>开奖时间</h2>\n<p>北京时间 3 月 14 晚 23 点</p>\n<h2>抽奖条件</h2>\n<p>评论即可参与抽奖，多次评论只会最早一次的评论生效</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://github.com/Licoy/utils.fun/raw/main/docs/index.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1773448340, "replies": 33, "id": 1198203}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 70054, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9582, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 93264, "username": "gefangshuai", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/gefangshuai", "website": "https://corebook.notion.site/", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75d1/38db/93264_mini.png?m=1772502993", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75d1/38db/93264_normal.png?m=1772502993", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75d1/38db/93264_large.png?m=1772502993", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75d1/38db/93264_xlarge.png?m=1772502993", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75d1/38db/93264_xxlarge.png?m=1772502993", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75d1/38db/93264_xxxlarge.png?m=1772502993", "created": 1421984093, "last_modified": 1772502993, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "remember5", "last_touched": 1773445000, "title": "自从用了 Claude Code， Intellij 家族的 ide 很少打开了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1198110", "created": 1773395287, "deleted": 0, "content": "**自从用了 Claude Code ，Intellij 家族的 ide 很少打开了**\r\n\r\n你们用什么工具配合 ai 工具呀？\r\n\r\n\r\n![]( https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lifedever/images@master/uPic/2026/03/qkb5bT.jpg)", "content_rendered": "<p><strong>自从用了 Claude Code ，Intellij 家族的 ide 很少打开了</strong></p>\n<p>你们用什么工具配合 ai 工具呀？</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lifedever/images@master/uPic/2026/03/qkb5bT.jpg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1773395287, "replies": 31, "id": 1198110}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_large.png?m=1650095354", "name": "security", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_normal.png?m=1650095354", "title": "信息安全", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/security", "topics": 2003, "footer": "", "header": "我们都希望自己管理的计算机系统在运转过程中不要遇到任何安全事件。只是，这个不完美的世界的现实告诉我们：学无止境。", "title_alternative": "Security", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_mini.png?m=1650095354", "stars": 2127, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 260, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 644798, "username": "ZettarYuFan", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ZettarYuFan", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9d15/8e4c/644798_mini.png?m=1764817237", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9d15/8e4c/644798_normal.png?m=1764817237", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9d15/8e4c/644798_large.png?m=1764817237", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9d15/8e4c/644798_xlarge.png?m=1764817237", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9d15/8e4c/644798_xxlarge.png?m=1764817237", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9d15/8e4c/644798_xxxlarge.png?m=1764817237", "created": 1692684788, "last_modified": 1764817237, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ShawnShi", "last_touched": 1773466648, "title": "广大 V 友注意， IDEA 插件 claude-code-gui 插件会盗刷 token，我已中招，已经举报下架", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1198130", "created": 1773400171, "deleted": 0, "content": "事情是这样的，我之前买了中转，想在 IDEA 上使用，填入中转 key 后，我有一段时间没用，再次上线时，发现被盗刷了 700 多的额度，现在该已经被举报下架了，我在他的 GitHub 留言了，大家以后注意这种情况，真的恶心。\r\n[Imgur]( https://imgur.com/onsnZMZ)\r\n[Imgur]( https://imgur.com/aeBh6QS)\r\n[Imgur]( https://imgur.com/n6xpyQQ)\r\n[Imgur]( https://imgur.com/hQdywG2)", "content_rendered": "<p>事情是这样的，我之前买了中转，想在 IDEA 上使用，填入中转 key 后，我有一段时间没用，再次上线时，发现被盗刷了 700 多的额度，现在该已经被举报下架了，我在他的 GitHub 留言了，大家以后注意这种情况，真的恶心。\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/onsnZMZ\" rel=\"nofollow\">Imgur</a>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/aeBh6QS\" rel=\"nofollow\">Imgur</a>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/n6xpyQQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">Imgur</a>\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/hQdywG2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Imgur</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1773459210, "replies": 29, "id": 1198130}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f340/f1b1/241_large.png?m=1747645886", "name": "lifestyle", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f340/f1b1/241_normal.png?m=1747645886", "title": "生活方式", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/lifestyle", "topics": 277, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Lifestyle", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f340/f1b1/241_mini.png?m=1747645886", "stars": 136, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 241, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 370899, "username": "ll5270", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ll5270", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/97b1f718483b05ce388b24e33efc7c71?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/97b1f718483b05ce388b24e33efc7c71?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/97b1f718483b05ce388b24e33efc7c71?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1545014646, "last_modified": 1755746484, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "AkinoKaedeChan", "last_touched": 1773405983, "title": "观热贴有感而发，如果可以的话，你想选择哪种人生？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1198088", "created": 1773390566, "deleted": 0, "content": "A：已婚，一线城市有房，背负百万以上房贷，工作 996 。\r\n\r\nB：已婚，二线城市，有房，有几十万贷款，工作 965 。\r\n\r\nC：未婚，三线城市有房，无贷款，存款百万 失业躺平。\r\n\r\n\r\n1：有娃\r\n\r\n2：无娃\r\n\r\n我选 B 和 1\r\n\r\n本来想把有娃没娃加在 ABC 上的，但是觉得不太合理,单独弄了一列。", "content_rendered": "<p>A：已婚，一线城市有房，背负百万以上房贷，工作 996 。</p>\n<p>B：已婚，二线城市，有房，有几十万贷款，工作 965 。</p>\n<p>C：未婚，三线城市有房，无贷款，存款百万 失业躺平。</p>\n<p>1：有娃</p>\n<p>2：无娃</p>\n<p>我选 B 和 1</p>\n<p>本来想把有娃没娃加在 ABC 上的，但是觉得不太合理,单独弄了一列。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1773395985, "replies": 28, "id": 1198088}]